   - Old: `CompactHashTable` for supplier_suppkey → nationkey mapping (requires hash computation + probing)
   - New: `std::vector<int32_t> supplier_nationkey_array[100001]` with direct index-based access
   - **Benefit**: Eliminates hash function overhead (~3-4 cycles/lookup) and provides O(1) guaranteed cache-friendly access
